
---

### `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Node modules
node_modules/
npm-debug.log
yarn-error.log
pnpm-lock.yaml
package-lock.json

# Environment variables
.env

# Build outputs
dist/
build/
.vite/

# MacOS files
.DS_Store

# Logs
*.log

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-workspace
*.sublime-project

# Misc
*.local